<item>
            <title>[LU-2002] config-sanity 55 and 56 test never complete</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2002</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running both test 55 and 56 for conf_sanity never complete. On the client side it gets to&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Started lustre-OST03ff&lt;br/&gt;
mount lustre on /lustre/barry.....&lt;br/&gt;
Starting client: barry-oss1: -o user_xattr,flock 10.37.248.61@o2ib1:/lustre /lustre/barry&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The important information is on the MDS were we get this error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[ 1996.398952] LustreError: 140-5: Server lustre-MDT0000 requested index 0, but that index is already in use. Use --writeconf to force&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.425233] LustreError: 12596:0:(mgs_llog.c:2731:mgs_write_log_target()) Can&apos;t get index (-98)&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.441183] LustreError: 12596:0:(mgs_handler.c:600:mgs_handle_target_reg()) Failed to write lustre-MDT0000 log (-98)&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.470043] LustreError: 15f-b: Communication to the MGS return error -98. Is the MGS running?&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.486065] LustreError: 14005:0:(obd_mount.c:1963:server_fill_super()) Unable to start targets: -98&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.502610] LustreError: 14005:0:(obd_mount.c:1760:server_put_super()) no obd lustre-MDT0000&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.518289] LustreError: 14005:0:(obd_mount.c:141:server_deregister_mount()) lustre-MDT0000 not registered&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.538505] Lustre: server umount lustre-MDT0000 complete&lt;br/&gt;
[ 1996.551214] LustreError: 14005:0:(obd_mount.c:2569:lustre_fill_super()) Unable to mount  (-98)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
